{"tid":1471306,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[813反思] Be Water, also be Smart","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:25:39.000Z","uid":273207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ed8aab5e24f06d161930aa631fb7203cfd4284","tid":1471306,"uid":273207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:40:02.000Z","msg":"[P牌仔, 由於每日出post 有限制, 所以一次過寫, 歡迎留言討論, 如果認同希望大家可以正皮, 推同share, 唔喜歡都可以比負皮] <br />\n<br />\n813 事情己經發生左，呢一刻我地應該<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">從錯誤中學習，Be water, also be Smart</span></strong>，先係我地呢一代香港人最勁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幾個重點我想講<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 一定要睇警犬出醜會（特別係問答環節）</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">「知己知彼，百戰百勝」</span></strong>，雖然班警犬係錄音機，但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>言談間其實透露左好多戰術</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似813咁，812出醜會先大方咁認有臥底，第二日就出現捉鬼大行動？因為呢個係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黑警既劇本</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n而喺問答環節，好多時睇清楚警犬既回答，其實就會知佢地弱點喺邊。因為<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">當人回避問題，或者一直重複相同答案，其實代表住佢<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">隱藏住一啲事實/講緊大話</span></span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做文宣，出醜會最重要既唔係警犬講左啲乜，而係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>針對佢隱藏住一啲事實/講大話煲大佢</strong></span>（呢個都希望俾傳媒朋友見到，感謝你地一直去問啲咁勁既問題，去攻破警犬防線）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而812鄧炳強既回答間，其實一直都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>卸緊膊落啲前線警員度</strong></span>，比如「我既指示係叫臥底唔會進行犯法行為」（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">內心：但佢地做左就唔關我事</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）同埋「戰術係咁，但最後執行都係落喺前線警員根據實際情況決定」（<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">內心：同樣係唔關我事</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<br />\n<br />\n即係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後事成，佢就可以領功；事敗，佢可以搵前線警員祭旗</span></strong>，自己立於不敗之地上。（唔知前線警犬有無咁既智慧去理解到）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家為止，其實警犬既誠信已經跌到好低，所以最近睇到<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">佢地既戰術亦都會係玩攬炒</span></strong>，誓要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「製造暴力」抹黑哂我地示威者，所以我地一定唔可以中計</span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 對付鬼既最好方法: 理性思維</span></strong><br />\n鬼其實就唔係今日先出現，前面都一直有。而<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>捉鬼屌鬼並唔係主線任</strong></span>，但既然警犬打左張咁明既「鬼」牌，我地該要識<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>利用番鬼去達成我地既主要目的 (五大訴求+國際/大陸文宣)</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.  睇下會唔會見到佢既行動方針, 再見招拆招 (如果見到懷疑「鬼」)<br />\n2. 做文宣, 有合理懷疑所有破壞性行動都係「鬼」做 (e.g. 阻人上機, 自己出手鬼打鬼)<br />\n3. 叫傳媒朋友黎影證據(樣+身分證), 影完就當「鬼」係condom 就OK</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中共最想既就係我地分化，估唔到邊個係「鬼」。但其實我地唔需要估，最重要係理性思維，睇「行動對我地有無幫助」，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我地而家最需要就係「民意＋國際聲音」</strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果行動會帶黎正面效果，無論係咪鬼都好，都要多謝佢；如果唔係，可以同佢理性解釋番就夠，佢唔聽就忽視佢（同多加留意\b佢會唔會喺現場做出破壞性行為）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「鬼」既最大特徵係聲大大，但又自己唔做野（free-rider）</span></strong>，所以如果之後喺唔同現場見到人聲大大，千忻唔好咁容易比現場情緒激發左，一定<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>要冷靜，觀察下</strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫得大聲需要聽既情況，暫時我都係諗到3個<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>1。「撒退/走啊」（當警犬衝出黎捉人）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2。「叫記者」（搵記者黎影底重要野）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3。「救人啊」（生命誠可貴）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以喺連登入面，其實真係唔<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>需要分鬼定人</strong></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地唔同被洗左腦既大陸人</strong></span>，唔係人話點做就點做，我地係識理性思考，做每一件事所帶黎既效果。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 唔好忽視鏡頭/傳媒既重要性：我地喺鏡頭係面向全世界</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當黑警都要諗辦法去避開鏡頭做衰野既時候, 我地<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">示威者同樣要注意番喺鏡頭前面既表現</span></strong>, 因為<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>傳媒係我地既盟友</strong></span>, 會幫我地影到好多黑警既罪證, 而同時都係會影住我地和平示威者既表現, 比全世界睇到. (而我地做緊既和平示威係光明正大, 根本唔需要避開鏡頭或者阻住記者朋友)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 未來方向：和理非＋國際文宣</span></strong><br />\n經過813，雖然被警犬/中共冼左一獲，但同時佢亦都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暴露左佢既手牌</span></strong>，亦都係文宣可以力搞<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 毋忘721, 811:</span></strong> 警犬搞813出黎，就係想用佢黎蓋過前面既事，而文宣要做就係繼續煲番前面事件，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>證明警犬前面做既野全部都係非法，證明813 事件都係警犬搞出黎屈我地示威者</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 813 內地鬼有傳媒同公安</span></strong>，可以做大佢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">證明中共勢力入侵香港</span></strong>，不論警隊有無同內地鬼割都好，對我地形勢都係做好。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>a. 警隊話唔關佢地事：</strong></span>即係中共已經跨過左香港警犬同政府，直接派人落黎，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>嚴重破壞香港一國兩制</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">b. 警隊話係佢地安排：</span></strong>即係前面既和平示威入面，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">充滿破壞性既行動都係警犬安排</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>3. 要做好國際文宣：承認813責任，再眾焦5大訴求（特別係雙普選）</strong></span><br />\n813 或多或少都影響到國際旅客，呢個必須要承認同作出補救。當政府/警犬一直唔認錯，回避大眾訴求既時候，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地示威者承認番責任會有助我地重建國際聲音</span></strong>，無論係咪鬼搞事，發生左唔愉快既事，我地都會有部份責任。<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地要做唔係學政府咁玩語言藝術，只係直接面對問題，做得唔好就要認</span></strong>。咁<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>先顯得政府/警犬有幾咁出醜。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">公關做得好，日後文宣戰場會更有利。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港加油！勝利在望！Be Water, also be Smart!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同意請幫手推上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n813「和你非」有感+未來方向<br />\n尋日都寫左少少，已請左人出post，請大家有時間都可以望望 求推 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467311/page/1</a>) <br />\n<br />\n811事件影片（有中英字幕，國際文宣必備）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9HlA2tbTuic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9HlA2tbTuic&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3e8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=7470cdc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9HlA2tbTuic</a>"},{"pid":"4480b713d9561db5b839da9dd075fbd14b8de006","tid":1471306,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YvdK1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YvdK1E.jpg&h=e1c38679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D83Sf8j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD83Sf8j.jpg&h=da01072f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JSeBHOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJSeBHOk.jpg&h=4d624e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7KeuxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7KeuxB.jpg&h=6eb7f2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95FtyZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95FtyZg.jpg&h=ecc3ae69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/caConSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcaConSC.jpg&h=d1559671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"890f754567bb31a12e0708994d9ea97510f1c4be","tid":1471306,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}